The Quintesson finally lifts himself from his work place. "His body is
repaired, but he is still in stasis lock" he said, finally having used up
the spare metal. Wildrider picks up Dead-End "Good, then you can get to
work on him, while I put Dead-End in the CR" he said pointing to Beastbox's
mutilated body. "Ill bring you some more parts" as he leaves for the CR
chambers.
